{"tid":418212,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)打機嗰陣個MON貶下貶下","createTime":"2017-09-29T11:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T14:39:08.000Z","uid":76255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6f75892452641361bd327a9757a5334192f0f2","tid":418212,"uid":76255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1V_eRztcTnsdnJ2b0VGcmx1SnM/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0B1V_eRztcTnsdnJ2b0VGcmx1SnM%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=O%2F2QtF72%2ByUTb5qDpHHNk%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=687b87de\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1V_eRztcTnsdnJ2b0VGcmx1SnM/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n各位巴打<br />\n我發現用部desktop打機嗰陣個MON會貶下貶下<br />\n一開始打嗰陣都無乜事<br />\n但打得耐嗰陣就會好似條片咁<br />\n每撳一下mouse就貶一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我部機同個Mon都係1個月前新買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我部機係用r5 1600, gtx 1070<br />\nmon係LG 24MP88<br />\n應該唔會係插唔好/hdmi線有問題<br />\n有無巴打可以幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該哂"},{"pid":"dceccb5f68a3d06c4abf858b1eaf4a2a9967b630","tid":418212,"uid":76255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"補充返<br />\n我塊底板係技姦ab350m<br />\n頭先重新裝過graphic card driver<br />\n但情況無好轉<br />\n仲要個MON眨左一下之後自己幫我熄埋game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4f1c5c9eba431a05d045443d586c9a59439b4c","tid":418212,"uid":33524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"個顯示卡driver試下用舊一版"},{"pid":"327262dc82ee2b361bbe49d54af62ec6e96889b3","tid":418212,"uid":76255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:39:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個顯示卡driver試下用舊一版</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂巴打你<br />\n不過都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}